overview:
CBG provides free product comparisons of capital equipment used by manufacturing, warehousing and distribution.

A data base of over 400 manufacturers and 10,000 product models will display the manufacturers and models after the user enters the desired product and key parameters. The user can request additional information and quotes, if desired. The web site contains all major manufacturers. It saves the user many hours of searching and comparing products for a specific need.
